    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/816384ded13d21e50a0ceb2d1a8539d4.poster.avif?t=1734096723\" width=630 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/816384ded13d21e50a0ceb2d1a8539d4.webm?t=1734096723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/816384ded13d21e50a0ceb2d1a8539d4.mp4?t=1734096723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jazzhands is a <strong>gesture controlled</strong>, <strong>action-based rhythm game</strong>. Restore harmony to a silenced galaxy as you refine your choreography through increasingly challenging levels. Destroy beats by channelling the power of your bare hands through <strong>only the eye of your webcam</strong>.   </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free demo featuring 3 distinct levels</strong> allowing you try before you buy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/734ac31b0b860a7d5814af485c67a4d2.poster.avif?t=1734096723\" width=630 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/734ac31b0b860a7d5814af485c67a4d2.webm?t=1734096723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/734ac31b0b860a7d5814af485c67a4d2.mp4?t=1734096723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jazzhands uses <strong>computer vision to interpret your gestures</strong> requiring only a webcam, avoiding the requirement of specialist VR hardware. This facilitates a <strong>unique mixed-reality experience</strong> that aims to <strong>remain accessible to most gamers</strong>. Jazzhands has been further optimized to work with a broad spectrum of devices, including those with <strong>less processing capabilities</strong>. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All you need to get started is a <strong>basic webcam</strong> or an <strong>integrated camera</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > There's <strong>no need for specialised VR or MR technology</strong>, or a high-end gaming device. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Offline, local and <strong>private</strong> - <strong>we don't store any footage</strong>, everything is live-time. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/ac5c0324dde12339e78b022629aadcb2.poster.avif?t=1734096723\" width=630 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/ac5c0324dde12339e78b022629aadcb2.webm?t=1734096723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/ac5c0324dde12339e78b022629aadcb2.mp4?t=1734096723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/fbd7874e4576af43df25e16b93e6ecc9.poster.avif?t=1734096723\" width=630 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/fbd7874e4576af43df25e16b93e6ecc9.webm?t=1734096723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/fbd7874e4576af43df25e16b93e6ecc9.mp4?t=1734096723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a galaxy once thriving with song, the mysterious Silent Composer has repressed all rhythm. Travel through 6 muted worlds <strong>meeting inhabitants</strong> and <strong>restoring missing melodies</strong> in a mission to <strong>extinguish the Composer's dark presence</strong>, and release his rhythmic grip. In this demo you will travel across 3 planets, performing to each one!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Distinctive worlds, each hosting a <strong>range of unique characters and lore</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Uncover the galaxy's secrets</strong> as you embark on an epic tour!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284720/extras/8231a935471f3cee6485c5410f2467aa.avif?t=1734096723\" width=630 height=220 /></span></p>",
